title: Tony Goldwyn / Daughter's Tonsillectomy
description: Sean’s A-Fib acts up again so he has to sneak out of a party to rush to the hospital. Priyanka explains trauma therapy with EMDR and Brainspotting. Tony Goldwyn shares his scary parent story when his 18 month old daughter needed a tonsillectomy.
author: info@hazymills.com (Hazy Mills Network)
